
================================================
SSH to Windows server 
================================================

Install optional features (settings > Apps > Optional Features)

	-open ssh server 
	-open ssh client

Then to services applet

	-Set open SSH startup to automatic

Set Firewall

	Powershell
		Get-NetFirewallRule -name *ssh*

tftp

Download Solarwinds TFTP

	Start 
	
	On Client

	-Turn winkdows features on or off > check TFTP client


	On server 

	Windows Firewall > allow another app > Browse
	
	-find the TFTP.exe  "System32 on both pc's

	-might have to add TFTPServer to allow, 
		and SolarWinds TFTP server in firewall

	(if running VM Nics, bind to all addresses)

	
